### Change 3: Transition Standardization (1 day)

**Approach:** Replace all transition classes with standard

**Pattern:**
```tsx
// OLD (various)
<div className="transition-colors">
<div className="transition-all duration-300">
<motion.div transition={{ duration: 0.3 }}>

// NEW (standard)
<div className="transition-all duration-standard ease-smooth">
<motion.div transition={{ duration: 0.2, ease: [0.4, 0, 0.2, 1] }}>
```

**Affected Files:**
- `src/components/Sidebar.tsx` - Already correct, keep as reference
- `src/widgets/Dashboard/BaseWidget.tsx` - Update Framer Motion duration: 0.3 → 0.2
- `src/components/Footer.tsx` - Update Framer Motion duration: 0.3 → 0.2
- All components with `transition-colors` (~180 occurrences)

**Standard Config (Reference):**
```js
// tailwind.config.js
transitionDuration: {
  standard: '200ms',  // Use this everywhere
}
transitionTimingFunction: {
  'ease-smooth': 'cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1)',  // Use this everywhere
}
```

