## Risks & Mitigation

| Risk | Impact | Probability | Mitigation |
|------|--------|-------------|------------|
| **Spacing changes break layout** | Medium | Low | Visual QA after each widget, daily regression |
| **Framer Motion timing feels wrong** | Low | Low | Test on real devices, adjust if needed |
| **Button height changes overflow containers** | Medium | Low | DevTools measurement, adjust container if needed |
| **Bundle size increases** | Medium | Low | Monitor after each commit, lazy load if needed |
| **TypeScript errors** | Low | Low | Type-check after each major change |
| **Navigation breaks after Planning link update** | High | Low | Test both Sidebar and Header links, verify route |

